Supreme Court — Appellate Term, June, 1900.

Before Beekman, P. J., Giegerich and O’Gorman, JJ.

Louis Rosenthal, Respondent, v. Jacob Rosenthal et al., Appellants. Appeal from a Judgment of the Municipal Court of the City of New York, borough of Manhattan. C. JL Schampain, for Appellants; J. Marks, for Respondent.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. No
